tva:BasicDescription.tva:Title: Kahani Comedy Circus Ki - Episode 49 - 19th August 2012 - Grand Final
tva:BasicDescription.tva:Synopsis: Get ready to ride on the roller coaster of laughter and fun as Comedy Circus is set to tickle your ribs with its fresh season, Kahani Comedy Circus Ki.This season essentially will go down the memory lane with the past successful seasons like Jadoo, Tansen, Circus, Teen ka Tadka as the themes for epsiodes... These themes will be seen as challenges for the contestants...
